003.name: Jason
003.text: I got a good haul today, the ricefish were hungry

005.name: Jason
005.text: Yeah, the RICEFISH, Where do you think rice comes from? You think it just grows on plants? No, I have to work hard to catch the ricefish. IT’S NOT AS EASY AS YOU THINK INTENSE PENETRATION.

007.name: Jason
007.text: you don’t understand. Rice is my life. Rice is my passion. I was born by the rice, and I will return to it. It is the way of the rice.

010.name: Jason
010.text: Make me a RiCe sandWhiCh and lets do something SHALLOW ( ͡° ͜ʖ ͡°)

013.name: Unknown
013.text: SKEEET SKEET BANG BANG MY HOMIE WHAT’S UP. I’M TELLIN YOU MY BOSS BE BALLIN WITH ALL THOSE BENJAMINS HE BE GIVIN ME AND MY CREW SO LET ME BREAK IT DOWN PLAYA. LET MY EMPLOYER COP YOUR CRIB, OR ELSE YOU’RE ABOUT TO CATCH THIS FADE

014.name: Jason
014.text: I’ve told you countless times and I’ll tell you again, I can’t sell the land. It means very much to me and AdA. If there’s anything you want please just take it, but let me keep my home.

015.name: Unknown
015.text: You’re making the wrong choice playa, I warned you….

016.name: Jason
016.text: Oh no, the other farmers, I have to go help them!
